# Financial Risk Management Capital Expense Reserve Adjusted Amount

## identifier
de4909

## type
float

## definition
Report the adjusted value of the expense reserve as determined in accordance with the management capital standard. This reflects capital requirements arising from expense risks in a closed fund scenario.

The adjustment is for the prescribed yield change in the discount rate used in their valuation, in accordance with the solvency standard.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.ManagementCapital.ExpenseReserveAdjusted.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
